message.body: @shakirgameing Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive:

commenter.name: yoj99
commenter.bio: Hello! I'm a Tekken competitor who mains Reina and previously Julia Chang. I've been competing for over 6 years now and stream a variety of things but you'll mostly see Tekken and occasionally I'll speedrun SM64. Hope you enjoy my content! :)

message.body: @yoj99 Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive: Typing

fragments.text: Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive: Typing
